{"word":"κιρνάω","slug":"κιρνάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κιρνάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:κεράννυμι'><el>κεράννυμι</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<p/><i>to mix</i> wine with water, in 3rd sg. <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>ἐκίρνα</el> and <el>κίρνη</el>, <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <el>κιρνάς</el>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>; in <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, 3rd sg. <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> <el>κιρνᾶι, 1</el>st <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <el>κίρναμεν.</el><p/>"}]}